  "notes": [
    "Pinned OCI SDK contract: CreateFleet, GetFleet, ListFleets, UpdateFleet, DeleteFleet, ChangeFleetCompartment, GetWorkRequest, ListWorkRequests, ListWorkRequestErrors, and ListWorkRequestLogs are present in v65.110.0. Create, update, and delete return opc-work-request-id without a Fleet body, while GetFleet and ListFleets project Fleet lifecycle and status fields directly.",
